<h1>Password Reset</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @user.first_name %>,</p>
<p>
Your password for <b><%= @user.name %></b> has been reset. Please visit the link below to
<%= link_to "reset", edit_password_reset_url(@user.reset_token, email: @user.email) %>
 your password.
</p>
<p>This link will expire in two hours.</p>
<p>
If you did not request your password to be reset, please ignore this email.
</p>

<p>
Thanks,<br>
Erin at Brandywine Furniture
</p>
